README for init directory. This directory contains mainly 'factory' code to help configure initial conditioins for state, initial conditions for external forcing, boundary conditions. 

For boundary conditions, there are 3 distinct tasks:

(1) specifying the conditions (gspecbdy_factory)
(2) initializing bdy conditions (ginitbdy_factory)
(3) updaating boundary conditions (gupdatebdy_factory)
